# Ignore everything under .claude/ EXCEPT project-scoped skills, which
# ship with the repo (their SKILL.md is part of the project's source
# of truth for adding new skill-specific landing pages). Note: the
# `.claude/*` pattern (not `.claude/`) is required so that the negation
# below can re-include subdirectories — git can't re-include files
# under a directory that was excluded as a whole.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
